Maintainer: Luis Osorio-Olvera <luismurao@gmail.com>
Description: Provides optimized C++ code for computing the partial ROC test used in niche and species distribution modeling. The implementation follows Peterson et al. (2008) <doi:10.1016/j.ecolmodel.2007.11.008>. Parallelization via OpenMP was implemented with assistance from the DeepSeek AI Assistant (<https://www.deepseek.com/>).
